// ── Daily narrative: built only from verified runCashflowBrainLocal /
// ── Minimal cashflow history buffer: last 5 ticks, final-output fields
// only (day30, runway, categoryDrift, timestamp). No raw transactions,
// no intermediate state, no v3/v4 fields. Lives on win since the engine
// functions themselves are pure and hold no state between calls. ────────
